{"tid":2321691,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"九章跟本唔係傳統意義上既電腦","createTime":"2020-12-11T16:48:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-14T01:22:20.000Z","uid":306109,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"c01068d92a6d3044e7bcc8a1107bcfcd83962b27","tid":2321691,"uid":306109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T16:48:28.000Z","msg":"正常電腦率玻色采樣係用數學式去計<br />\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200602200006563.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg-blog.csdnimg.cn%2F20200602200006563.png&h=4eaa9434&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九章係用物理方法出左個大概既答案再推算番個積和式<br />\n<br />\n就好似人地叫你計個角既角度係幾多，你就直接令量角器去度，咁緊係快啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人地計個數要幾千萬年，你直接用物理方法采樣度出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n算法都唔同，九章同電腦無可比性，D記者文盲炒作<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申:睇唔明條公式<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b8940725ca57ce485a62abf0d02b0e3d9f99bc6","tid":2321691,"uid":328994,"like":2,"dislike":13,"score":-11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T16:54:52.000Z","msg":"廢話，量子電腦梗係唔係傳統意義上嘅電腦啦"},{"pid":"ca58853ea94304c429fad2e865dcadb9961a1806","tid":2321691,"uid":181156,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T16:59:00.000Z","msg":"唔明<br />\n咁如果可以直接度出黎咁有咩問題?<br />\n<br />\n利申：唔識it"},{"pid":"a39f81c48d7f7a0f06c2d4ad5e4ce20505513879","tid":2321691,"uid":306109,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9b8940725ca57ce485a62abf0d02b0e3d9f99bc6","tid":2321691,"uid":328994,"like":2,"dislike":13,"score":-11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T16:54:52.000Z","msg":"廢話，量子電腦梗係唔係傳統意義上嘅電腦啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T17:01:09.000Z","msg":"I meant 佢唔係電腦亦都唔係傳統既量子電腦，只係一個率高斯玻色采樣既工具，計唔到其他野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"506d55555b64e1f1d71eb8a1ef26667647236326","tid":2321691,"uid":306109,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca58853ea94304c429fad2e865dcadb9961a1806","tid":2321691,"uid":181156,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T16:59:00.000Z","msg":"唔明<br />\n咁如果可以直接度出黎咁有咩問題?<br />\n<br />\n利申：唔識it"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T17:11:13.000Z","msg":"例如一間大學入邊有2000個學生，有40%既學生係男性，咁男性平均數咪0.4xn=0.4x2000=800人，咁簡單就可以用數學方式計出黎，但係積和式係非常複雜，超級電腦都要計幾千萬年。<br />\n<br />\n而九章就好醒唔去計，直接去采樣，即係去間大學度抽樣，當佢抽左100個人，點知有50人係男人，咁代唔代表到成間大學?想出黎個數有代表性就要抽多D人先會接近0.4。"},{"pid":"02c8796d82e3b6fecb6ae86cbd0b9ebb3bab033a","tid":2321691,"uid":82628,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T17:15:54.000Z","msg":"傳統電腦用算式模擬實驗<br />\n九章係直接做實驗"},{"pid":"ddaf9d09e63df2a071a364e7420cc9fc2c73461c","tid":2321691,"uid":306109,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02c8796d82e3b6fecb6ae86cbd0b9ebb3bab033a","tid":2321691,"uid":82628,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T17:15:54.000Z","msg":"傳統電腦用算式模擬實驗<br />\n九章係直接做實驗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T17:17:33.000Z","msg":"算式計出黎個數係絕對值<br />\n<br />\n九章實驗出黎個數係估算值"},{"pid":"03a2362ef276f7eae8a8538d7dcb99c3e2c36f2b","tid":2321691,"uid":119729,"like":10,"dislike":6,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T17:19:44.000Z","msg":"九章打出要包晒"},{"pid":"a5482a4b8609859e4ace582e78db86279e587444","tid":2321691,"uid":263485,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T02:00:43.000Z","msg":"Analog 電腦比 Digital 電腦屌打幾十年後，重新大反攻。"},{"pid":"5a60025f5f01b5bb788e7a102ed6573ef101f674","tid":2321691,"uid":100760,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T02:59:45.000Z","msg":"正常電腦喺excel打=1+1，會點計<br />\n如果九章有excel，喺入面打=1+1，又會點計？點體現到九章計得快啲"},{"pid":"484af8001589dbd41f9e2d8a9cbd66d4e